snippet.textDisplay: I've been listening to this song since the day it was released in YouTube... Heard it countless times... I don't know what is it about this song that keeps bringing me back... I don't think it's a song... I feel this is more than just a song... it's a story, a movie, a life... Life of every daughter and the father... May be the fact that my father leaves away from me makes me love this piece of art more and more... I still remember the first time I heard this song, after the second part of the letter I felt tears on my cheek... I cried like a baby the second time I heard the song... Can't express my feelings about the songs... Just LOVE It... Love From Bangladesh! Hats off to The Lyricist and Writer... 💗💗💗
